{"tid":740680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉波逝世一週年 支聯會舉辦燭光晚會","createTime":"2018-07-13T05:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T05:46:39.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1731cae959168aed6388905086e5fca05c110d","tid":740680,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1889374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1889374%2F&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2fc3507f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1889374/</a><br />\n<br />\n為悼念諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波逝世一周年，支聯會今晚8時於金鐘添馬公園舉行追思會。去年劉曉波離世，支聯會舉辦燭光遊行，吸引2500人參與，當時已促請北京停止軟禁其遺孀劉霞，如今劉霞獲准遠赴德國，重獲自由，原定晚上集會其中一項內容是全球聯署爭取「釋放劉霞」行動，將可轉化為給予對方的祝福。"},{"pid":"009d9b51fae335b2b5ce5813487be92799740d15","tid":740680,"uid":39381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"又要捐款<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4835e7332f990ea5c0f9af4f2b0c4a9a6dba3d22","tid":740680,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"Cap水時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}